# .NET Backend
**/bin/
**/obj/
backend/InterviewIQ.API/interviewiq.db
backend/InterviewIQ.API/interviewiq.db-journal
backend/InterviewIQ.API/interviewiq.db-shm
backend/InterviewIQ.API/interviewiq.db-wal

# Node.js Frontend
**/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
